00:00:21,200 --> 00:00:22,100
Beth!
Beth!

5
00:00:22,400 --> 00:00:23,100
Coming.
来了.

6
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:26,100
Sorry.
对不起.

7
00:00:27,200 --> 00:00:29,100
Hey, didn't you have a soccer game today?
Hey,今天你不是有足球赛吗?

8
00:00:29,300 --> 00:00:30,400
What was the score?
比分如何?

9
00:00:30,500 --> 00:00:31,400
Four to...
4比...

10
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:36,600
Tell them you are eating dinner and will call back later.
告诉他们你在吃饭, 过会儿再打给他们.

11
00:00:38,700 --> 00:00:39,900
You see what I mean?
你明白我的意思吗?

12
