Dad! It's for you.
爸爸!你的电话.

13
00:00:46,800 --> 00:00:47,600
Sorry.
对不起.

14
00:00:49,600 --> 00:00:52,100
The phone is driving me crazy.
这电话真让我发疯.

15
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:54,800
Mom, we should just turn on the answering machine.
妈妈,我们应该打开电话留言机.

16
00:00:55,100 --> 00:00:57,500
I don't want to use it to screen calls.
我不想用电话留言来筛选电话.

17
00:00:57,560 --> 00:00:58,650
I don't think it's right.
我认为这样做不妥.

18
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:00,800
If we're home, we should answer the phone.
如果我们在家,我们应该接电话.

19
00:01:01,300 --> 00:01:02,850
